item.title: Cant connect to my rsps
item.dc:creator: @The_Web_Guy The Web Guy
item.description:
@The_Web_Guy wrote:

  1. Must be port-forwarded.
  2. Client must connect to the IP that the server is running on, if you’re running it localhost, make sure it’s connecting to localhost.
